<div class="content-body">

<p>
  Hey, I'm Solivas. This is my little corner of the internet — a digital garden where I write,
  think out loud, and collect ideas that interest me.
</p>

<p>
  A digital garden is different from a blog. Posts here aren't finished essays — they're living
  notes that get updated, revised, and grow over time. Some things are half-baked thoughts,
  others are more developed. All of it is genuinely mine.
</p>

<h2>What you'll find here</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Blog</strong> — longer, more considered writing</li>
  <li><strong>Notes</strong> — short observations and micro-thoughts</li>
  <li><strong>Ideas</strong> — concepts I'm exploring, in various stages of growth</li>
</ul>

